              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve invoices associated with a specific payment number where the notification email has not been sent. It logs the operation details and handles exceptions by logging errors and optionally sending an email notification. The procedure is part of the "
